<h2 id="character-level-text-generation-with-lstm">Character-level Text Generation with LSTM</h2>
<p><a href="https://github.com/christopheberle/LSTM-text-generation"><img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/GitHub-View_on_GitHub-blue?logo=GitHub" alt="View on GitHub" /></a>
<a href="https://github.com/christopheberle/LSTM-text-generation/blob/main/nlp.ipynb"><img src="https://img.shields.io/badge/Jupyter-Open_Notebook-blue?logo=Jupyter" alt="Open Notebook" /></a></p>

<p><strong>Abstract</strong></p>
<div style="text-align: justify">I build a character-level LSTM recurrent neural network (RNN) capable of generating new texts character-by-character. The network was trained on H.P. Lovecraft's short stories.</div>
